		"description": "On Android devices (2.3.x thru 4.3), convertPointToView() return null for point in ImageView (contained in a ListView) translating to coordinates of the ListView.\r\n\r\nBehavior is correct in iOS.\r\n\r\n{code:xml}\r\nlist.xml:\r\n<ListView id=\"list\">\r\n   <Templates>\r\n      <ItemTemplate name=\"template1\">\r\n         <ImageView bindId=\"image\" id=\"img\" onSingletap=\"doClick\"/>\r\n      </ItemTemplate>\r\n   </Templates>\r\n</ListView>\r\n{code}\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nlist.js:\r\nfunction doClick(e){\r\n   var pt = { x: e.source.rect.x, y: e.source.rect.y };\r\n   var newPt = e.source.convertPointToView(pt, $.list);  // newPt == null (Android only)\r\n}\r\n{code}",
		"attachment": [],
